            "id": 5898590,
            "title": "《異動股》紫金升逾2%領漲金礦股,關稅風險推升金價",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社13日專訊》紫金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02899:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02899\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02899-HK</a>)H股現價升2.5%,報16.48元,以現價計,該股暫連升2日,累計升幅6%。該股成交約1619萬股,涉資2.65億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　美國關稅不確定性因素持續令市場不安,憂慮高關稅將會引發通脹升溫,避險需求提升帶動金價上漲,隔晚紐約期金再升近1%,於2950美元關口前徘徊,現報約2945美元。港股<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>ETF　SPDR金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02840:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02840\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02840-HK</a>)現升0.8%,報2103元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　金礦股造好;山東<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01787:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01787\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01787-HK</a>)升1%,報15.96元;招金礦業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01818:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01818\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01818-HK</a>)升0.3%,報14.24元;靈寶<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(一千)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03330-HK</a>)升4%,報5.72元;赤峰<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06693:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06693\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06693-HK</a>)升1.8%,報13.88元;潼關<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00340-HK</a>)升7.6%,報0.85元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報23521,跌79點或跌0.3%,主板成交逾328億元。國企指數報8656,跌25點或跌0.3%。恒生科技指數報5802,跌42點或跌0.7%。即月期指新報23554,跌85點,高水33點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>紫金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02899:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02899\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02899-HK</a>)</td><td>16.48元</td><td>升2.49%</td></tr><tr><td>山東<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01787:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01787\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01787-HK</a>)</td><td>15.96元</td><td>升1.01%</td></tr><tr><td>招金礦業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01818:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01818\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01818-HK</a>)</td><td>14.24元</td><td>升0.28%</td></tr><tr><td>靈寶<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(一千)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03330-HK</a>)</td><td>5.72元</td><td>升4.00%</td></tr><tr><td>赤峰<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06693:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06693\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06693-HK</a>)</td><td>13.88元</td><td>升1.76%</td></tr><tr><td>潼關<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00340-HK</a>)</td><td>0.85元</td><td>升7.59%</td></tr><tr><td>中國<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAGUSDOZ\">白銀</a>集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00815:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00815\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00815-HK</a>)</td><td>0.40元</td><td>升8.11%</td></tr><tr><td>SPDR金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02840:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02840\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02840-HK</a>)</td><td>2103.00元</td><td>升0.81%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　(hc)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
